sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Blind User
    participant LK as LiveKit WebRTC
    participant AG as Agent (agent.py)
    participant DG as Deepgram STT (cloud)
    participant VR as VoiceRouter
    participant LFM as LiveFrameManager
    participant FO as FrameOrchestrator
    participant PP as PerceptionPipeline (local GPU)
    participant SG as SceneGraphBuilder
    participant SF as SpatialFuser
    participant VQA as VQAReasoner
    participant OL as OllamaHandler
    participant CLOUD as qwen3.5:cloud (Ollama cloud runtime)
    participant EL as ElevenLabs TTS (cloud)
    participant ST as StreamingTTSCoordinator

    Note over U,ST: Flow 1: Voice Query → Vision Analysis → Speech Response

    U->>+LK: Voice + Camera stream (WebRTC)
    
    par Audio Path
        LK->>+AG: Audio frames (real-time)
        AG->>+DG: Audio stream (WebSocket)
        DG-->>-AG: Transcribed text
        AG->>+VR: classify_intent(text)
        VR-->>-AG: RouteResult{intent, handler, confidence}
    and Video Path
        LK->>AG: Video frames (real-time)
        AG->>+LFM: push_frame(frame)
        LFM-->>-AG: TimestampedFrame
    end

    alt Intent = VISUAL_DESCRIBE / VISUAL_IDENTIFY
        AG->>+FO: process_frame(frame)
        
        par Parallel Perception (Local GPU - ONNX CUDA EP)
            FO->>+PP: detect(image)
            PP-->>-FO: List[Detection]
        and Depth Estimation (Local GPU)
            FO->>+PP: estimate_depth(image)
            PP-->>-FO: DepthMap
        and OCR (if text visible)
            FO->>+PP: ocr_read(image)
            PP-->>-FO: OCR text
        end
        
        FO->>+SG: build_scene_graph(detections, depth, masks)
        SG-->>-FO: SceneGraph
        FO->>+SF: fuse(perception_result)
        SF-->>-FO: List[ObstacleRecord]
        FO-->>-AG: FusedFrameResult

        AG->>+VQA: answer(question, scene_data, image)
        VQA->>+OL: chat_completion(prompt, image_b64)
        OL->>+CLOUD: POST /v1/chat/completions (async HTTP)
        
        alt Success
            CLOUD-->>-OL: LLM response
            OL-->>-VQA: response text
            VQA-->>-AG: VQA answer
        else Timeout / Error
            CLOUD--x OL: timeout (10s)
            OL-->>VQA: fallback response
            VQA-->>AG: "I couldn't analyze that clearly"
        end
    
    else Intent = SPATIAL_OBSTACLE / SPATIAL_HAZARD
        AG->>+FO: process_frame(frame)
        FO->>+SF: fuse(perception_result)
        SF-->>-FO: List[ObstacleRecord] sorted by priority
        FO-->>-AG: FusedFrameResult

        Note over AG: MicroNavFormatter generates TTS cue
        AG->>AG: format_navigation_cue(obstacles)
    
    else Intent = GENERAL_CHAT
        AG->>+OL: chat_completion(text)
        OL->>+CLOUD: POST /v1/chat/completions (async HTTP)
        CLOUD-->>-OL: response
        OL-->>-AG: answer text
    end

    AG->>+ST: speak(response_text)
    ST->>+EL: synthesize(text)
    EL-->>-ST: audio stream
    ST-->>-AG: audio chunks
    AG->>LK: Audio response (WebRTC)
    LK-->>-U: Spoken response

    Note over U,ST: Error Recovery Path

    rect rgb(255, 235, 235)
        Note over AG,CLOUD: If LLM fails after 2 retries
        AG->>AG: Use cached/template response
        AG->>ST: speak(fallback_message)
        ST->>EL: synthesize(fallback)
        EL-->>ST: audio
        ST-->>AG: audio chunks
        AG->>LK: Fallback audio
    end
